text: Trolls World Tour (also known as Trolls 2) is a 2020 American animated jukebox musical fantasy comedy movie. It was produced by DreamWorks Animation and Universal Pictures. A sequel to Trolls and the second installment in the series, it was directed and written by Walt Dohrn. It stars the voices of Anna Kendrick, Justin Timberlake, Rachel Bloom, James Corden, Ron Funches, Kelly Clarkson, Anderson .Paak, and Sam Rockwell. It was followed by Trolls Band Together. == Voice cast == * Anna Kendrick as Queen Poppy * Justin Timberlake as Branch * Rachel Bloom as Queen Barb * James Corden as Biggie * Ron Funches as Cooper * Kelly Clarkson as Delta Dawn * Anderson .Paak as Darnell * Sam Rockwell as Hickory * George Clinton as King Quincy * Mary J. Blige as Queen Essence * Kenan Thompson as Tiny Diamond * Kunal Nayyar as Guy Diamond * Icona Pop as Satin and Chenille * J Balvin as Tresillo * Flula Borg as Dickory * Ester Dean as Legsly * Jamie Dornan as Chaz * Gustavo Dudamel as Trollzart * Gwen Stefani as DJ Suki * Walt Dohrn as Smidge, Fuzzbert, King Peppy, Cloud Guy == Other websites == * * * * * * Category:2020 animated movies Category:DreamWorks Animation movies Category:American sequel movies Category:2020s sequel movies
